## Troubleshooting

### Gallery Won't Open

**Check:**
- Models have been generated
- Press B key when not typing
- Generator UI is closed first

**Solution:**
```javascript
// In console
window.modelGallery.show()
```

### Model Not Showing

**Causes:**
- Model not fully loaded
- Viewing from inside model
- Lighting issue

**Solutions:**
- Click Reset View button
- Zoom out with scroll wheel
- Check model actually exists in list

### Performance Issues

**If Gallery is Slow:**
- Disable auto-rotate
- Close other applications
- Reduce browser zoom
- Limit number of models

### Controls Not Working

**Check:**
- Gallery is focused (click preview area)
- Not conflicting with other UI
- Mouse is over preview panel

