## Technical Details

### Rendering

**Engine:** Three.js WebGL Renderer
- **Scene:** Isolated from main game
- **Camera:** Perspective, 50° FOV
- **Controls:** OrbitControls with damping
- **Shadows:** PCF soft shadows

**Lights:**
```javascript
Ambient: 0xffffff, 60%
Directional: 0xffffff, 80% from (5, 10, 7)
Fill: 0x4dd0ff, 30% from (-5, 5, -5)
```

**Grid:**
```javascript
GridHelper(10, 10, 0x4dd0ff, 0x333366)
Opacity: 30%
```

### Performance

**Optimizations:**
- Model cloning for preview (original untouched)
- Separate render loop (runs only when open)
- Efficient material updates
- Auto-cleanup on close

**Benchmarks:**
| Models | Load Time | FPS |
|--------|-----------|-----|
| 1-5 | <100ms | 60 |
| 6-10 | <200ms | 60 |
| 11-20 | <500ms | 50+ |

### Memory Usage

**Per Model:**
- Geometry: 1-5MB
- Textures: 1-8MB
- Metadata: <1KB

**Total Gallery:**
- Scene: ~2MB
- Renderer: ~5MB
- Controls: <1MB

